s, what are the shipping methods?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>All our products are software-based. You can download your software through our portal after the purchase process is completed.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"ddd199e\"},{\"_id\":\"8ca24fc\",\"tab_title\":\"How Do I Place an Order?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>You can place your order from our website after registering. Browse the product you need, add it to your cart, and then proceed to checkout and you are all set to go.<\\/p>\"},{\"_id\":\"fe369e3\",\"tab_title\":\"Is it compulsory to have an account for placing orders?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Yes, you would need to make an account to place an order.<\\/p>\"},{\"_id\":\"18f35ed\",\"tab_title\":\"How often do I need to update my antivirus software?\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Our antivirus software automatically detects new updates and will inform you about them. You can also simply grant permission for automatic updates while setting up the software.<\\/p>\"}],\"title_html_tag\":\"h4\",\"faq_schema\":\"yes\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"title_typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"title_typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":25,\"sizes\":[]},\"title_typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]},\"title_typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"title_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"20\",\"right\":\"20\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"20\",\"isLinked\":true},\"icon_align\":\"right\",\"icon_space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0,\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"40\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"accordion\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]');
