8217;s most accurate filter yet</p>\n<p>Two-Way Firewall</p>\n<p>Shut out hackers and prevent malicious software from exploiting your OS or stealing your information</p>\n<p>Network Intrusion Security</p>\n<p>Find out if someone is stealing your Internet connection�My Home Network shows you all your connected devices</p>\n<p>Advanced Web Protection</p>\n<p>Know if a site you&#8217;re about to visit is dangerous with McAfee SiteAdvisor��just look for the red, yellow, and green safety ratings<br />\nStay protected from phishing URLs in email and instant messages with the SiteAdvisor� LIVE add-on</p>\n			<div style=\"padding-bottom:15px;\" class=\"wordads-tag\" data-slot-type=\"belowpost\">\n				<div id=\"atatags-dynamic-belowpost-689fd1eae4857\">\n					\n				</div>\n			</div>\n<div id=\'jp-relatedposts\' class=\'jp-relatedposts\' >\n	<h3 class=\"jp-relatedposts-headline\"><em>Related</em></h3>\n</div>\";s:3:\"url\";s:114:\"https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com/product/mcafee-total-protection-1-year-1-device/\";s:5:\"image\";s:138:\"https://i0.wp.com/antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/McAfee-Total-Protection-2018-500x500-2.webp?fit=500%2C500&quality=80&ssl=1\";s:13:\"itemCondition\";s:31:\"https://schema.org/NewCondition\";s:3:\"sku\";s:7:\"SKU-007\";s:6:\"offers\";a:1:{i:0;a:8:{s:5:\"@type\";s:5:\"Offer\";s:3:\"url\";s:114:\"https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com/product/mcafee-total-protection-1-year-1-device/\";s:5:\"price\";s:5:\"30.00\";s:13:\"priceCurrency\";s:3:\"USD\";s:18:\"priceSpecification\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"price\";s:2:\"30\";s:13:\"priceCurrency\";s:3:\"USD\";}}s:15:\"priceValidUntil\";s:25:\"2025-09-15T00:33:46+00:00\";s:6:\"seller\";a:3:{s:5:\"@type\";s:12:\"Organization\";s:4:\"name\";s:18:\"Antiviruspoint.org\";s:3:\"url\";s:65:\"https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com\";}s:12:\"availability\";s:29:\"https://schema.org/OutOfStock\";}}}}');
