edesigned home screen that supports touch-friendly devices.</li>\n<li><strong>ENHANCED�Reports�</strong>Quickly understand how your protections are securing your data and system.</li>\n<li><strong>PC Tune-up�</strong>Remove unused applications, cached browser files, and other junk to speed up your PC.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n			<div style=\"padding-bottom:15px;\" class=\"wordads-tag\" data-slot-type=\"belowpost\">\n				<div id=\"atatags-dynamic-belowpost-68baf52d44d06\">\n					\n				</div>\n			</div>\n<div id=\'jp-relatedposts\' class=\'jp-relatedposts\' >\n	<h3 class=\"jp-relatedposts-headline\"><em>Related</em></h3>\n</div>\";s:3:\"url\";s:107:\"https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com/product/mcafee-antivirus-1-year-1-pc-tss/\";s:5:\"image\";s:124:\"https://i0.wp.com/antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/McAfee-AV-1PC-500x500-1.webp?fit=500%2C500&quality=100&ssl=1\";s:13:\"itemCondition\";s:31:\"https://schema.org/NewCondition\";s:3:\"sku\";s:7:\"SKU-039\";s:6:\"offers\";a:1:{i:0;a:8:{s:5:\"@type\";s:5:\"Offer\";s:3:\"url\";s:107:\"https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com/product/mcafee-antivirus-1-year-1-pc-tss/\";s:5:\"price\";s:5:\"44.99\";s:13:\"priceCurrency\";s:3:\"USD\";s:18:\"priceSpecification\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"price\";s:5:\"44.99\";s:13:\"priceCurrency\";s:3:\"USD\";}}s:15:\"priceValidUntil\";s:25:\"2025-10-05T14:35:25+00:00\";s:6:\"seller\";a:3:{s:5:\"@type\";s:12:\"Organization\";s:4:\"name\";s:18:\"Antiviruspoint.org\";s:3:\"url\";s:65:\"https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com\";}s:12:\"availability\";s:26:\"https://schema.org/InStock\";}}}}');
